      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7455428730971693254, guid: 59be40fb5c6fecf43ba904ca6bbaeadd, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Oh shit..
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7455428730971693254, guid: 59be40fb5c6fecf43ba904ca6bbaeadd, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: Sorry I thought this was umamusume
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7455428730971693254, guid: 59be40fb5c6fecf43ba904ca6bbaeadd, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[2]'
      value: I also need to buy deodorant, my kitten says I smell too much.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7455428730971693254, guid: 59be40fb5c6fecf43ba904ca6bbaeadd, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[3]'
      value: Could you pwease win Plinko for me? I would be oh so happy pwincess.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7455428730971693254, guid: 59be40fb5c6fecf43ba904ca6bbaeadd, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[4]'
      value: If you don't want me to eat your legs right fucking now you better go
        find me a maple bourbon bbq whopper.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7455428730971693254, guid: 59be40fb5c6fecf43ba904ca6bbaeadd, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[5]'
      value: I used to eat those when I had to take my dumb chud kids to Burger King
        before I lost the custody battle.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7455428730971693254, guid: 59be40fb5c6fecf43ba904ca6bbaeadd, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[6]'
      value: Now, find me that JUICY burger or I'm gonna ground your beef.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8932679997703117976, guid: 59be40fb5c6fecf43ba904ca6bbaeadd, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
